cz.cuni.mff.d3s.trupple.parser

Class NodeFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.d3s.trupple.parser.NodeFactory

  • public class NodeFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Factory for our nodes. The Parses use it to create nodes for currently parsed rules. It also contains current state and identifiers table.
